  "api_usage_guidance": {
    "high_confidence_required_fields": [
      "datasource",
      "viz_type",
      "granularity_sqla",
      "time_range",
      "metrics"
    ],
    "recommended_always_set": [
      "time_grain_sqla",
      "adhoc_filters",
      "groupby",
      "row_limit",
      "comparison_type",
      "color_scheme",
      "y_axis_format",
      "annotation_layers"
    ],
    "api_field_examples": [
      "granularity_sqla",
      "time_grain_sqla",
      "metrics",
      "groupby",
      "timeseries_limit_metric",
      "time_compare",
      "comparison_type",
      "rolling_type",
      "resample_rule",
      "annotation_layers"
    ],
    "avoid_confusion": [
      "不要把 Compare 当成标准 chart data API 图表去套 `/api/v1/chart/data` 的 `query_context` 模板；当前图真实入口是 legacy `/superset/explore_json/`。",
      "不要把 runtime 别名 `comparisonType`、`xAxisFormat`、`yAxisBounds`、`annotationLayers` 写回 root form_data。",
      "不要把 `comparison_type` 误写成 `period`、`dimension` 或 `show_percent_change` 一类并不存在于源码的字段；当前正式枚举只有 `values`、`absolute`、`percentage`、`ratio`。",
      "`time_compare` 是 `multi=true` + `freeForm=true` 的相对时间偏移数组，预置选项写法是 `1 year`、`52 weeks` 这类自然语言，不是固定只读枚举。",
      "当 `time_compare` 有值时，必须显式提供一个能解析成封闭区间的 `time_range`，否则后端会拒绝生成 time shift 查询。"
    ]
  }
}
